| Moment | Screen | What Happens | Output |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | 1.1 | Context re-anchor | Founder re-oriented to stage, vision, sprint frame |
| 1 | 1.2 | Four-sprint arc view | Founder sees where Q1 sits in the annual narrative |
| 1 | 1.3 | Directional focus prompt | Founder selects the framing for their sprint goal |
| 1 | 1.4 | Sprint goal drafting | Founder authors their sprint goal |
| 1 | 1.5 | Reality check | Founder pressure tests the goal against four criteria |
| 1 | 1.6 | Sprint goal locked | Sprint goal saved — becomes persistent north star |
| 2 | 2.1 | Sprint Board entry | Nine capabilities pre-loaded from Quarter Map |
| 3 | 3.0 | Capability context | Founder oriented to capability before creating initiatives |
| 3 | 3.1A/B/C | Initiative creation | Tiered forms — Prioritize, Plant, Iterate |
| 4 | 4.1 | Sprint Board full review | All initiatives visible, summary strip present |
| 4 | 4.2 | Pre-lock review | Three reflection questions, deprioritized capabilities named |
| 5 | 5.1 | Loading state | Synthesis generating |
| 5 | 5.2 | Sprint posture synthesis | Full completion moment — synthesis, summary, PDF, launch CTA |

